test.doc: Validates the registration flow of a new user using valid data. Precondition: User must not be already registered. Test Steps: 1. Navigate to the SignIn/SignUp Screen. 2. Enter valid data in all required fields: name, email, and password. 3. Submit the registration form. Expected Result: User is successfully registered and redirected to the Home Screen.
